### signal-cli REST API
### See https://bbernhard.github.io/signal-cli-rest-api/

@baseUrl = {{$dotenv SIGNAL_CLI_BASE_URL}}
@phoneNumber = {{$dotenv SIGNAL_CLI_PHONE_NUMBER}}

### Send a message to self (mirrors SendMessage_ToSelf_ReturnsTimestamp)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v2/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv SIGNAL_CLI_AUTH}}

{
  "message": "REST client test message",
  "number": "{{phoneNumber}}",
  "recipients": [
    "{{phoneNumber}}"
  ]
}

### Get version and build info (mirrors GetAbout_ReturnsVersionInfo)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/about
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv SIGNAL_CLI_AUTH}}

### Get configuration (mirrors GetConfiguration_ReturnsConfiguration)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/configuration
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv SIGNAL_CLI_AUTH}}

### Receive pending messages (mirrors ReceiveMessages_ReturnsMessages)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/receive/{{phoneNumber}}
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv SIGNAL_CLI_AUTH}}

### List accounts (mirrors ListAccounts_ReturnsAccounts)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/accounts
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv SIGNAL_CLI_AUTH}}

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/health
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv SIGNAL_CLI_AUTH}}
